Hi <%= @appointment.person.name %>,

<% if (@appointment.starts - Date.today).to_i != 1 %>
This is a reminder for your upcoming shift beginning in <%= pluralize (@appointment.starts - Date.today).to_i, "day" %>.
<% else %>
This is a reminder for your shift beginning tomorrow.
<% end %>

- Calendar: <%= @appointment.calendar.title %>
- Start Date: <%= @appointment.starts.strftime("%B %-d, %Y") %>
- End Date: <%= @appointment.ends.strftime("%B %-d, %Y") %>
<% if @appointment.note != "" %>
- Notes: <%= @appointment.note %>
<% end %>

Please let the shift coordinator (<%= (@appointment.calendar.watchers.split(/\s*,\s*/)).to_sentence %>) know immediately if you are unable to make your scheduled shift.

Thanks,
The Shift Coordinator
